  "detailed_description": "\"Paper Plane\" is a difficulty 2D shooting game with hilarious  atmosphere;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA combination of “Shoot Them Up” and “Parkour” gameplay style;<br />\r\nYou need to get enough fuel by shooting as many as enemies to reach the goal;<br />\r\nWith more than 50 challenging stage areas and 5 BOSS Fights;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMost animations and characters were drawn by Office Excel and sound FX recorded by voice acting, mixed by morden electronic music；<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat a bizarred and novel experience;",
  "about_the_game": "\"Paper Plane\" is a difficulty 2D shooting game with hilarious  atmosphere;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA combination of “Shoot Them Up” and “Parkour” gameplay style;<br />\r\nYou need to get enough fuel by shooting as many as enemies to reach the goal;<br />\r\nWith more than 50 challenging stage areas and 5 BOSS Fights;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMost animations and characters were drawn by Office Excel and sound FX recorded by voice acting, mixed by morden electronic music；<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat a bizarred and novel experience;",
